      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Adventurer's Armory 2 pg. 9</em></p><h3><span title=\"PFS Legal\">[PFS]</span> Statistics</h3><p><strong>Cost</strong> 35 gp <strong>Weight</strong> 3 lbs.</p><p><strong>Damage</strong> 1d4 (small), 1d6 (medium); <strong>Critical</strong> x2; <strong>Range</strong> 30 ft.; <strong>Type</strong> P; <strong>Special</strong> see text</p><p><strong>Category</strong> Ranged; <strong>Proficiency</strong> Exotic</p><p><strong>Weapon Groups</strong> Spears; Thrown</p><h3>Description</h3><p>This single-use javelin bears a thunderstone just behind the head. If you successfully strike a target with one of these javelins, the creature takes damage as normal and is the center of the thunderstone's effect. If you miss, roll to see where the javelin lands (as if determining a miss with a splash weapon); that square becomes the center of the thunderstone's effect.</p>"
